description: The final scene of Nutts for Butts pits the legendary Asoka (you saw him in Probe and begged for more) with a new comer named Chris Neal. Neal, who lives down south, came to us with a wide smile that was full of Dixie charm, but it was his amazing butthole that caught our eye. Talk about a stunning scene--one with more action than you can absorb in one viewing! This is what fisting is all about--a huge hairy paw, a smooth muscle butt, and a gaping hole winking for service! Don't hesitate!
title: Fistpack 4 - Nuts For Butts
